{"abstract": "Mr. Rosenblat, a survivor of Nazi camps, wrote a tale of a kind girl and an apple that turned out to be false.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2015/02/22/business/media/herman-rosenblat-85-dies-made-up-holocaust-love-story.html", "snippet": "Mr. Rosenblat, a survivor of Nazi camps, wrote a tale of a kind girl and an apple that turned out to be false.", "lead_paragraph": "The first curse on mankind was imposed because of an apple, and for all that happened to Herman Rosenblat in his 85 years \u2014 the horrors inflicted in Nazi concentration camps, the gunshot wound he suffered when his Brooklyn television repair shop was robbed, the global fame bestowed by two appearances on \u201cThe Oprah Winfrey Show\u201d \u2014 it is an apple for which he will be most remembered. That first bite of the fruit was built on a lie.", "print_section": "A", "print_page": "22", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/02/22/business/22OBITSROSENBLAT/22OBITSROSENBLAT-articleLarge-v2.jpg", "height": 400, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2015/02/22/business/22OBITSROSENBLAT/22OBITSROSENBLAT-articleLarge-v2.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 400}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/02/22/business/22OBITSROSENBLAT/22OBITSROSENBLAT-jumbo-v2.jpg", "height": 682, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/02/22/business/22OBITSROSENBLAT/22OBITSROSENBLAT-superJumbo-v2.jpg", "height": 1365, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/02/22/business/22OBITSROSEN